name: Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide total returns consisting principally of interest income. The fund investing primarily in floating rate and other short term debt securities of Canadian and foreign issuers. In order to achieve its investment objective, Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF invests primarily in floating rate and other short term debt securities of Canadian and foreign issuers. Investments are not constrained by credit ratings except that, at time of purchase, at least 75% of the market value of Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF will be comprised of securities rated BBB or higher (`investment grade) (or their equivalent in the opinion of the portfolio manager).
fulldescription: The ETF seeks to provide total returns consisting principally of interest income. The fund investing primarily in floating rate and other short term debt securities of Canadian and foreign issuers. In order to achieve its investment objective, Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF invests primarily in floating rate and other short term debt securities of Canadian and foreign issuers. Investments are not constrained by credit ratings except that, at time of purchase, at least 75% of the market value of Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF will be comprised of securities rated BBB or higher (`investment grade) (or their equivalent in the opinion of the portfolio manager). Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETFs investments will also tend to be concentrated in debt securities with a term-to-maturity of five years or less although it could hold debt securities with a longer term to maturity as long as the weighted average term-to-maturity of all the securities held in the portfolio at the time of purchase is less than five years. Lysander-Canso Floating Rate ActivETF will be actively managed and may use derivatives in accordance with NI 81-102.
